{"tid":1888940,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"油塘紀律部隊宿舍有警員初步確診","createTime":"2020-02-20T13:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T16:56:31.000Z","uid":197005,"like":128,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"da13c2ce4d1d0de0750da4bf1d3e864da1a5fe40","tid":1888940,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"據悉，一名於觀塘普通科門診求診後，再自行留唾液送交測試的病人，樣本測試初步呈陽性反應，正被安排入聯合醫院隔離治療。醫管局由19日起擴大新型冠狀病毒檢測範圍，為症狀輕微的急症室及普通科門診病人進行檢測，由病人自行留唾液再交回急症室或門診進行測試。今次是首次門診化驗而確診個案。據悉患者居於油美苑潤美閣紀律部隊宿舍，是一名紀律部隊人員，傳是警務人員。據悉他最近出席了一個退休聚會，有超過60人參加。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7HV42cn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HV42cn.gif&h=928503bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8422084bee17a7d08cc2bb32eaba12e8d6401d97","tid":1888940,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"狂賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7dbdfb33a5470564cd11128e573ea4658bf592","tid":1888940,"uid":265179,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"最強黃絲示範打狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67c5869562cc803f117756d126f25deaff8a39b","tid":1888940,"uid":28223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 